Rodent & non-rodent species (rat, dog, NHP)
Required for IND-enabling package""" .

vtx:result a vtx:LabWorkflowEntity ;
    rdfs:label "Result" ;
    vtx:expressedAs vtx:result_datum ;
    rdfs:comment """Assay output — quantitative measurement or qualitative observation
BAO assay result component / AFO result namespace""" .

vtx:result_datum a vtx:LabWorkflowEntity ;
